history.content:
Hello Everyone!

 

Data Science Society at Berkeley is a student-run organization that provides resources for all data science-related content and further this already booming field.

 

A central event that our organization holds is the annual Berkeley Data Science Panel. This year, we will be having 5 leading industry figures from the following companies...

  • Tesla
  • Airbnb
  • Affirm
  • Celmatix

 

In addition, Division of Data Sciences very own Director of Programs - Anthony Suen - will be sharing insights from his past experience and current work with the Division. Come for a chance to learn from industry leaders, network with professionals, and utilize our resume drop on Nov. 18th, 10:30am - 2:00pm, at West Pauley Ballroom.

 

For more information, visit... 

https://www.eventbrite.com/e/2018-berkeley-data-science-panel-tickets-51953078055
